Description:

Join NBA Champion Channing Frye (@channingfrye) and Emmy Award-winning co-host Dan Sheldon (@DanSheldonVoice) for this season of Talkin' Blazers. Talkin' Blazers has a unique take on everything Rip City with the insight and opinions of a former member of the Portland Trail Blazers. New episodes drop weekly. Subscribe and download today.
